      "Text": "Security update for dovecot22",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for dovecot22 fixes the following issues:\n\nSecurity issue fixed:\n\n- CVE-2017-15130: Fixed a potential denial of service via TLS SNI config\n  lookups, which would slow the process down and could have led to exhaustive\n  memory allocation and/or process restarts (bsc#1082828)\n\nThis update was imported from the SUSE:SLE-12:Update update project.",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
